    • handlerMove

      public boolean handlerMove​(Model model, GodCardController controller, PlayerMove move)
      Artemis can move twice but not in the starting cell This method controls if it's the first time it moves and it asks if you want to use the power. If this is the second time the player moves, it controls if the used worker is the same, the selected cell is not the one from which it moved and then resets the flags and makes a normal move.
      Overrides:
      handlerMove in class GodCard
      Parameters:
      model - is the game model
      controller - is the game controller
      move - is the move message received by the view
      Returns:
      false only if this is the second time the player moves and every error control is negative
